That happened to me in Philadelphia on the 71- had 20 degrees of free 
play suddenly!  The housing holding the swing lever bushing rots out and 
separated.  I welded steel 1/8" x 3/4"  around it like a cage criss 
crossed over top and bottom and it held up OK until I found a new front 
beam.

